  {name: "Welcome Contractor", subject: "Welcome to Select Home Warranty", body: "Dear {contractor company}, \n<br/><br/>\nThank you for taking an interest in becoming a vendor for Select Home Warranty, a leader in the \nhome warranty industry. Your role as a service provider will go a long way in assuring our customers' \nsatisfaction.  \n<br/><br/>\nPlease take a minute to complete all attached materials.\n<br/><br/>", locked: true, attachments: nil, reply_to: nil},
  {name: "Price Quote", subject: "Your Price Quote", body: "<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Let's face it, life happens. When important home systems or appliances break down, we're there to help arrange for their repair or replacement quickly, easily and affordably.</p>\r\n<p>Home protection plans can save thousands; stay ahead of the unexpected with Select Home Warranty</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 214px;\" width=\"552\" cellspacing=\"8\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\">{image logo}</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\"><strong>Quote:</strong></td>\r\n<td>{customer contract_number}</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\"><strong>Customer Name:</strong></td>\r\n<td>{customer name}</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\"><strong>Coverage Address:</strong></td>\r\n<td>{customer full_address}</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\"><strong>Coverage:</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>{customer package_name} plan for ${customer pay_amount} annually</strong> <br /><strong> <span class=\"gray\">{customer package_covers}</span></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td>{customer coverage_option_names}</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><br />What you can expect from Select Home Warranty:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Call or email 24 hours a day, 365 days a year to request service</li>\r\n<li>Our customers use their contract an average 2+ times per year</li>\r\n<li>No limit to the number of covered repairs we will pay for during your contract term</li>\r\n<li>Select maintains a network of over 10,000 professional and insured service contractors</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>A leader in the home warranty industry. A service network that is second to none. It's no secret why home owners are choosing Select Home Warranty to help manage the high costs of home repairs.</p>\r\n<p><br /> If you have any questions, please call me at <strong>1-855-267-3532</strong>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"indent_30\">Thank You,</p>\r\n<p class=\"indent_30\"><strong>{my name}</strong></p>\r\n<p>{image logo}</p>\r\n<p align=\"CENTER\"><a href=\"https://www.onlinebusinessbureau.com/Companyrating.cfm?Company_ID=1843450\"><object id=\"SealTracker\" width=\"80\" height=\"124\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"https://fpdownload.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,0,0\" align=\"middle\">\r\n<param name=\"allowScriptAccess\" value=\"sameDomain\" />\r\n<param name=\"movie\" value=\"https://www.onlinebusinessbureau.com/SealTracker.swf?Company_ID=1843450\" /><param name=\"quality\" value=\"high\" /><param name=\"bgcolor\" value=\"#ffffff\" /><embed src=\"https://www.onlinebusinessbureau.com/SealTracker.swf?Company_ID=1843450\" quality=\"high\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" width=\"80\" height=\"124\" name=\"SealTracker\" align=\"middle\" allowScriptAccess=\"sameDomain\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" pluginspage=\"https://www.macromedia.com/go/getflashplayer\" />\r\n</object></a></p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "Contractor Assigned", subject: "Contractor Assigned to Select Home Warranty Claim {customer contract_number}", body: "<p>{image logo}</p>\r\n<p>Dear {customer name},<br /><br />Your request for service has been assigned to&nbsp;<strong>{contractor company}</strong>, an authorized Select Home Warranty service technician. Please allow up to 48 hours for the contractor to reach out to you.<br /><br />If you do not hear from them within 48 hours please contact&nbsp;<strong>{contractor company}</strong>&nbsp;at&nbsp;<strong>{contractor phone}</strong>&nbsp;to schedule a mutually convenient service appointment.<br /><br />If you do not have an appointment scheduled with your authorized contractor within 48 hours, please call us at&nbsp;<strong>{installation phone}</strong>,&nbsp;option 2, so that we may assist you in getting an appointment scheduled.<br /><br />Please remember that upon the technician&rsquo;s arrival you will be required to pay the&nbsp;<strong>{the service_charge}</strong>&nbsp;service call fee. Should you have any questions feel free to call our claims department at&nbsp;<strong>{installation phone}</strong>.<br /><br />Thank you,</p>\r\n<p><br />Select Home Warranty<br />Claims Department<br /><a href=\"mailto:claims@selecthomewarranty.com\">claims@selecthomewarranty.com</a></p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: "claims@selecthomewarranty.com"},
