  {name: "Maintenance Records", subject: "Current Claim", body: "Dear Valued Customer,<br>\n\nPlease be advised that your claim is presently pending in our system. We require more information to proceed with your claim \t\t\t\t Contract :\n\t\t\t\t{customer contract_number}.<br> At this time, we are requesting that you supply additional information on the unit in question (i.e. maintenance records/reports, repair records/invoices, etc.) You may fax them to {installation fax}  Attention: Claims Department; or email them to claims@selecthomewarranty.com. Please note, if your claim is time sensitive, poses health concerns, or may result in further damages if not immediately repaired, Select Home Warranry encourages you to have the repairs done out of pocket. You may then submit the above info, along with paid invoice, to be reviewed for possible reimbursement. If you have further questions or concerns, please call us Monday through Friday, 10am to 5pm Eastern Standard Time at {installation phone} option 2 and ask for a claims manager so that we may assist you further.<br>\n\nThank you,<br>\n\nSelect Home Warranty<br>\n\nClaims Department\n", locked: false, attachments: nil, reply_to: nil},
