y questions and for our latest available promotions, please call us at <strong>1-855-267-3532.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>{image logo}</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a title=\"trustedsiteseal80 by bsaban, on Flickr\" href=\"http://www.onlinebusinessbureau.com/Companyrating.cfm?Company_ID=1843450\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7318/9734269503_73ec7b1218_t.jpg\" alt=\"trustedsiteseal80\" width=\"65\" height=\"100\" /></a> <a title=\"url by bsaban, on Flickr\" href=\"../../../quote\"><img src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3776/9735492454_b9958c79bc_t.jpg\" alt=\"url\" width=\"83\" height=\"66\" /></a></p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "Refund Request", subject: "Refund Request", body: "<p>Dear Customer,<br /> Contract : {customer contract_number}.<br /> <br />Thanks for contacting us here at Select Home Warranty.</p>\r\n<p><br />Your policy has been canceled and your refund request has been processed. Depending on your financial institution it may take up to 10-14 business days to apply the funds back to your account.</p>\r\n<p><br /> If you have any questions please don&rsquo;t hesitate to email us at info@selecthomewarranty.com</p>\r\n<p><br />Thank You <br />Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "Zip Code Not Covered", subject: "Zip Code Not Covered", body: "<br>Thank you for your interest in a home warranty through Select Home Warranty. We do NOT currently offer coverage in your ZIP code. If your credit card has been charged, you will be receiving a full refund within 5-7 business day. </br>\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\r\nWe do add new ZIP codes from time to time and will contact you should your ZIP be added.</br>\r\n</p>\r\n<br>Thank you </br>\r\n<br>Select Home Warranty</br>", locked: false, attachments: nil, reply_to: nil},
  {name: "Adam info", subject: "select home warranty contact info", body: "<br>It was a pleasure speaking to you today about your interest in a home warranty plan through Select Home Warranty. \r\nBelow is my contact information, if I can be of any additional help please don't hesitate to email or call me. </br>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n<br>Adam Buck </br>\r\n<br>1-855 267 3532 Ext 42 </br>\r\n\r\n<br>adam@selecthomewarranty.com</br>\r\n\r\n<br>Regional Sales Manager</br>", locked: false, attachments: nil, reply_to: nil},
  {name: "Contract", subject: "Select Home Warranty, Thank you for enrolling", body: "<p>{image logo}</p>\r\n<p>{customer name},</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for enrolling in a warranty from Select Home Warranty. Before your card is charged a customer service rep will contact you to confirm your order.</p>\r\n<p>Should you need to make a service call, Please send an email to claims@selecthomewarranty.com.</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your business!</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "Need More Info", subject: "re: claim review", body: "Dear <p>{customer name},</p><br>\r\n\r\nPlease be advised that your claim for Contract :\r\n\t\t\t\t{customer contract_number} is presently pending in our system. We require more information to proceed with your claim.\t\t\t\t <br>  Please call us at 1-855 267 3532 for our claims department. <br>\r\n\r\nThank you,<br>\r\n\r\nSelect Home Warranty<br>\r\n\r\nClaims Department\r\n", locked: false, attachments: nil, reply_to: nil},
  {name: "not effective", subject: "New Claim", body: "<p>Dear {customer name},</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for submiting your claim. We have tried to process your claim for policy \#{customer _contract_number} but the policy is not yet effective for claims. You signed up with us less then 30 days ago and the policy does have a 30 day grace period before claims can be made, this is in section 4. of your contract. This policy only covers things that start after the 30 day grace period. You may have someone come down on your own and any repairs that you do can be submitted to the review department for possible partial reimbursement. The company usually is very generous with reimbursements during the non effective period.</p>\r\n<p>If you have any questions or would like to discuss this further please don't hesitate to email or call us at 1-855 267 3532.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank you</p>\r\n<p>Claims Department</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: nil},
  {name: "Cancellation Email, no refund", subject: "Your cancellation request", body: "<p>Dear {<a href=\"40\">customer first_name</a>} ,</p>\r\n<p>Contract : {customer contract_number}.</p>\r\n<p>Thanks for contacting us here at Select Home Warranty. My name is Chris and I'm happy to assist you today.</p>\r\n<p>We have received your request for cancellation and your policy is cancelled effective immediately.</p>\r\n<p>If you have any questions please don&rsquo;t hesitate to email me at info@selecthomewarranty.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank You,</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: nil},
