eseal80 by bsaban, on Flickr\" href=\"http://www.onlinebusinessbureau.com/Companyrating.cfm?Company_ID=1843450\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3697/9732260827_2c3da444d9_t.jpg\" alt=\"trustedsiteseal80\" width=\"51\" height=\"78\" /></a> <a title=\"url by bsaban, on Flickr\" href=\"../../../quote\"><img src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3776/9735492454_b9958c79bc_t.jpg\" alt=\"url\" width=\"83\" height=\"66\" /></a><img src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3795/10998697296_923aa20a13.jpg\" alt=\"CA_Sheild\" width=\"74\" height=\"74\" /></p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "New Proforma ", subject: "Proforma Invoice {customer contract_number}", body: "<p><a title=\"Header_3 by bsaban, on Flickr\" href=\"http://selecthomewarranty.com/plans\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7394/9404134082_b58390a986.jpg\" alt=\"Header_3\" width=\"629\" height=\"229\" /></a></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>Let's face it, life happens. When important home systems or appliances break down, we're there to help arrange for their repair or replacement quickly, easily and affordably.</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Home protection plans can save thousands; stay ahead of the unexpected with <span style=\"color: #000066;\">Select Home Warranty</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<h3>{the service_charge}</h3>\r\n<table style=\"height: 211px;\" width=\"599\" cellspacing=\"8\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\" width=\"115\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Quote:</strong></span></td>\r\n<td width=\"414\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">{customer contract_number}&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Buyer Name:</strong></span></strong></td>\r\n<td>{customer name}</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>Coverage Address:</strong></span></td>\r\n<td><span style=\"color: #000000;\">{customer full_address}</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\"><strong>Plan Selected:</strong></td>\r\n<td>{customer package_name}</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"label\" height=\"73\"><strong>Plan Details:</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<table border=\"1\" width=\"550\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"275\"><strong>Plan for ${customer pay_amount}&nbsp;</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"238\"><strong><span class=\"gray\">{customer package_covers}</span></strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong> {customer coverage_option_names}<br /> </strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><strong>Please Send </strong><strong>Check To:</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\">Select Home Warranty <br /> One International Blvd. <br />Suite 400 <br />Mahwah, NJ 07495-0400</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">info@selecthomewarranty.com</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;What you can expect from <span style=\"color: #000066;\"><a href=\"http://selecthomewarranty.com/plans\"><strong>Select Home Warranty</strong></a>:</span></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Savings:</strong>\r\n<p>You'll typically pay just one low deductible for covered components that need repair or replacement,* saving you hundreds or even thousands of dollars.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Convenience:</strong>\r\n<p>We're available 24/7/365. Our Customer Care representatives will assess your needs and match you with a pre-screened service professional, so you won't need to waste time searching through the phone book and hoping for the best.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Peace of Mind:</strong>\r\n<p>A&nbsp;<a href=\"http://selecthomewarranty.com/plans\">Select Home Warranty </a>provides assurance that you won't have to worry when a covered system or appliance breaks down, and that you will be provided with a repair professional you can trust.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">A leader in the home warranty industry. A service network that is second to none. It's no secret why home owners are choosing <strong><strong><span style=\"color: #000066;\">Select Home Warranty</span></strong> </strong>to help manage the high costs of home repairs.</span></p>\r\n<p>If you have any questions, please call me at <strong><span style=\"color: #000066;\">1-855-267-3532</span></strong>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"indent_30\"><span style=\"color: #000066;\">Thank You,</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"indent_30\"><span style=\"color: #000066;\"><strong>{my name}</strong></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>{image logo}</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a title=\"trustedsiteseal80 by bsaban, on Flickr\" href=\"http://www.onlinebusinessbureau.com/Companyrating.cfm?Company_ID=1843450\"><img src=\"http://farm8.staticflickr.com/7318/9734269503_73ec7b1218_t.jpg\" alt=\"trustedsiteseal80\" width=\"57\" height=\"88\" /></a> <a title=\"url by bsaban, on Flickr\" href=\"../../../quote\"><img src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3776/9735492454_b9958c79bc_t.jpg\" alt=\"url\" width=\"83\" height=\"66\" /></a><img src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3795/10998697296_923aa20a13.jpg\" alt=\"CA_Sheild\" width=\"79\" height=\"79\" /></p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "Grant_Web_Access", subject: "You have been granted web access to SelectHomeWarranty. ", body: "<p>{image logo}</p>\r\n<p>Hello {customer name},</p>\r\n<p>To login to your account, please <a href=\"../../../login\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a> and enter the username and password below.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; Username:<strong> {customer _contract_number}</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; Password: <strong>{the password}</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank you,</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty.</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "Renewal email", subject: "re:your home warranty policy", body: "<p><br />Dear {customer first_name} ,&nbsp;<br />Contract : {customer contract_number}.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This is a friendly reminder that your Select Home Warranty is expiring soon. This year you had the peace of mind knowing that your major home systems and appliances were protected against common failures. In the coming years you will find that a home warranty pays off even more. The beauty of a home warranty is it repairs or replaces items that will eventually fail. Your Select Home Warranty will protect you from these inevitable costs as long as your warranty is active.</p>\r\n<p>Make sure to renew your home warranty before it expires otherwise you will have a lapse in coverage and lose out on the discounted renewal rate. Please reply to this email or call us at 1-855-267-3532 option 1 for questions and to renew your Select Home Warranty.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank you,</p>\r\n<p>Renewal Department</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>\r\n<p>Phone:&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:1-855-267-3532\" target=\"_blank\">1-855-267-3532</a></p>\r\n<p>Fax: <a href=\"tel:1-732-490-6612\" target=\"_blank\">1-732-490-6612</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.selecthomewarranty.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.selecthomewarranty.<wbr />com</a></p>\r\n<p>One Less Worry</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "requested refund call billing", subject: "Your cancellation request", body: "<p><br />Dear {customer first_name} , <br /> Contract : {customer contract_number}.</p>\r\n<p>Thanks for contacting us here at Select Home Warranty.</p>\r\n<p>My name is Chris and I'm happy to assist you today.</p>\r\n<p>We have received your request for cancellation, please call our billing department at 1 855 267 3532. If you have any questions please don&rsquo;t hesitate to email me at <a href=\"mailto:info@selecthomewarranty.com\">info@selecthomewarranty.com</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank You,</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: "billing@selecthomewarranty.com"},
  {name: "Refund Confirmation", subject: "Refund Confirmation", body: "<p>Dear Customer,<br />Contract : {customer contract_number}.<br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>Per your request, your credit card has been refunded and your policy cancelled.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br />If you have any questions or if the credit does not show up within 3-5 days please don&rsquo;t hesitate to email us at info@selecthomewarranty.com</p>\r\n<p><br />Thank You&nbsp;<br />Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "Reimbursement Confirmation", subject: "Reimbursement Confirmation", body: "<p>Dear</p>\r\n<p>{customer name},</p>\r\n<p>Contract : {customer contract_number}.</p>\r\n<p>Per your policy, your claim reimbursement has been processed, credits can take up to 7-10 days to show up on your statement. If you have any questions please don&rsquo;t hesitate to email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@selecthomewarranty.com\">info@selecthomewarranty.com </a></p>\r\n<p>Thank You</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "HW Review", subject: "1 month free- from select home warranty", body: "<p>Dear {customer first_name},</p>\r\n<p><br />We hope that your recent experience with us was a positive one. Your feedback is very important to us. If you were satisfied with your recent service call please share your experience with others by clicking the link below, scroll to the bottom and rate us. Positive feedback really helps us out. You will receive 1 free month of service by doing so. If for any reason you weren't completely satisfied please email us and we will do our best to make it right.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.homewarrantyreviews.com/reviews/select-home-warranty#.Unpa4BCzLl8\">http://www.homewarrantyreviews.com/reviews/select-home-warranty</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank You,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "Referral Email", subject: "Earn A Free Month from Select Home Warranty", body: "<p><img alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Earn-A-Free-Month-When-You-Refer-A-Friend by select_homewarranty, on Flickr\" href=\"http://selecthomewarranty.com/plans\"><img src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3730/10746219174_cbc796611b.jpg\" alt=\"Earn-A-Free-Month-When-You-Refer-A-Friend\" width=\"182\" height=\"66\" /><img id=\"__mcenew\" alt=\"\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a title=\"CA_Sheild by select_homewarranty, on Flickr\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/108106198@N06/10998697296/\"><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3795/10998697296_923aa20a13.jpg\" alt=\"CA_Sheild\" width=\"76\" height=\"76\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a title=\"auth by select_homewarranty, on Flickr\" href=\"http://www.authorize.net/\"><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"http://farm3.staticflickr.com/2891/10745915946_a865ec04d1.jpg\" alt=\"auth\" width=\"91\" height=\"78\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.onlinebusinessbureau.com/Companyrating.cfm?Company_ID=1843450\"><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3790/10745838045_7bbedd686c.jpg\" alt=\"OBB\" width=\"57\" height=\"87\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a style=\"text-align: justify;\" title=\"referal_email by select_homewarranty, on Flickr\" href=\"http://selecthomewarranty.com/plans\"><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3717/10745816284_dec3bee9ce.jpg\" alt=\"referal_email\" width=\"573\" height=\"741\" /></a></p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "need to talk to customer", subject: "re:claim review", body: "<p>Dear {customer name},</p>\r\n<p>Please be advised that your claim for Contract : {customer contract_number} is presently in our system. We did need to speak with you, please call us at 1-855 267 3532 for our claims department.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank you,</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>\r\n<p>Claims Department</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "CA Review", subject: "Your recent Experience", body: "<p>Dear {customer first_name},</p>\r\n<p><br />We hope that your recent experience with us was a positive one. Your feedback is very important to us. If you were satisfied with our customer service, please share your experience with others by clicking the link below, and rate us. Positive feedback really helps us out. You will receive 1 free month of service by doing so. If for any reason you weren't completely satisfied please email us and we will do our best to make it right.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial; font-size: small;\"><a title=\"https://www.consumeraffairs.com/brands/16367/submit_review/\" contenteditable=\"false\" href=\"https://www.consumeraffairs.com/brands/16367/submit_review/\">https://www.consumeraffairs.com/brands/16367/submit_review/</a></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank You,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
  {name: "API Approval", subject: "API Request Approval", body: "<p>{image logo}</p>\r\n<p>Hello {partner fullname},</p>\r\n<p>You API access request has been approved.</p>\r\n<p>To login to your account, please click here: {partner partner_url}</p>\r\n<p>Username: &nbsp; {partner login}<br />Password: &nbsp; &nbsp;{partner password}</p>\r\n<p>To start using the API, please login:</p>\r\n<p>API Token: &nbsp;{partner api_token}<br />API docs: &nbsp; &nbsp;{partner api_documentation}</p>\r\n<p>Thank you,</p>\r\n<p>Select Home Warranty</p>", locked: false, attachments: "", reply_to: ""},
