  {slug: "plans", html: "      <h2>I'm Interested...</h2>\n      \n      <h4>But how much will I really save?</h4>\n      <p>With Select's annual or monthly payment options, you can significantly reduce the out-of-pocket repair expenses simply by becoming a customer! Without a plan from Select Home Warranty you could face staggering repair costs as high as $1300 and maybe more!</p>\n"},
  {slug: "homeownercenter", html: "    <h2>Homeowner Center</h2>\n\n    <p>Unfortunately, the appliances and home system components around our homes will eventually break down. Select Home Warranty will help you get it repaired or replaced by a qualified service contractor.</p>\n\n    <p>A home warranty is your best defense against these sudden breakdowns. It's not your homeowner's insurance policy. A home warranty is a separate contract covering repairs and replacements on systems and appliances in your home.</p>\n\n    <p>A home warranty can be very beneficial and can save you time and money when it is utilized for its intended purpose which is to cover your homes' systems and appliances for normal wear and tear. With over 10,000 license and pre-screened contractors, Select Home Warranty is prepared to make these sudden breakdowns stress free.</p>\n\n    <p>We offer 3 simple plans and easy monthly payment options to fit your budget. We've got you covered!</p>\n"},
  {slug: "buyingandselling", html: "<h2>Buying &amp; Selling Your Home</h2>\n\n<table style=\"width: 100%\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding-right: 15px\">\n<h3>Home Buyer</h3>\n    <p>A Select Home Warranty plan allows you to never again worry about the high cost of repairing or replacing your home's appliances or systems. You will not have to search any directories for contractors or repair technicians or wonder whether you can trust an unfamiliar service vendor.</p>\n\n    <p>When a covered item breaks down due to normal wear and tear, simply dial our toll-free number or email us at <a href=\"mailto:|||INSTALLATION_CLAIMS_EMAIL|||\">|||INSTALLATION_CLAIMS_EMAIL|||</a> and an authorized service technician will be dispatched by our knowledgeable customer service representatives to handle your needs. You will receive a follow up email with the Contractor's Name and phone number so that you may contact them directly to set up an appointment. Our experience will save you both time and money.</p>\n\n    <p>The other added benefits are: \n      <ul>\n        <li>Ease of knowing that we will replace a covered component if the service provider can not repair it.</li>\n        <li>Vast national network of licensed, certified, and pre-approved service contractors.</li> \n        <li>Exceptional rates on our Home Warranty Coverage Plans.</li> \n        <li>Service Providers that are very knowledgeable and ready to work for you.</li>\n        <li>Our low Service Call Fees (usually $60 depending on your state).</li>\n        <li>Payment plans to fit your budget.</li>\n      </ul>\n    </p>\n\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding-left: 15px\">\n<h3>Home Seller</h3>\n    <p>A home protection plan can be an effective marketing tool, instantly giving buyers additional confidence in their purchase. We can also help protect your home's systems and appliances while your home is on the market. Allowing you to focus on your next home instead of the one you are trying to sell.</p>\n    <p><ul>\n        <li>8 out of 10 buyers prefer to buy a home with a warranty.<sup>1</sup></li>\n        <li>Homes with warranties return a sales price that averages 3% higher.<sup>2</sup></li>\n        <li>Homes on the market with a warranty included sell on average 50% faster than homes without.<sup>3</sup></li>\n    </ul></p>\n\n    <ul class=\"footnotes\">\n      <li><sup>1</sup> Business Week Magazine</li>\n      <li><sup>2</sup> Gallup Poll</li>\n      <li><sup>3</sup> National Home Warranty Association</li>\n    </ul>\n\n</td>\n</tr></table>\n"},
  {slug: "realestate", html: "  <h2>Real Estate Professionals</h2>\n\n    <p>A home protection plan can be an effective marketing tool, instantly giving buyers additional confidence in their purchase.</p>\n\n    <p><ul>\n        <li>Homes with warranties return a sales price that averages 3% higher.<sup>1</sup></li>\n        <li>8 out of 10 buyers prefer to buy a home with a warranty.<sup>2</sup></li>\n        <li>Homes on the market with a warranty included sell on average 50% faster than homes without.<sup>3</sup></li>\n    </ul></p>\n\n    <p>As a Real Estate Professional, there is nothing better than a quick closing and the knowledge that the home that is sold is protected after the sale. A Real Estate Sales Broker or Agent can protect their clients and reputation by ensuring that every home they sell is protected by Select Home Warranty. \nFrom the feedback that we have received, we have noticed that realtors and sellers have sold homes quicker and most times at a increased price as buyers feel more confident in buying homes that have a Home Warranty Coverage Plan.</p>\n\n    <ul class=\"footnotes\">\n      <li><sup>1</sup> Business Week Magazine</li>\n      <li><sup>2</sup> Gallup Poll</li>\n      <li><sup>3</sup> National Home Warranty Association</li>\n    </ul>\n"},
  {slug: "contractors", html: "<h2>Contractor</h2>\n\n    <p>A relationship with Select Home Warranty can potentially help increase your customer base and cash flow while at the same time reduce your need for advertising.</p>\n\n    <p>Benefits of working with Select Home Warranty include:\n      <ul>\n        <li>Free leads. We'll send business to you. Our customer base is more than a million strong.</li>\n        <li>Free advertising. Select Home Warranty puts you face-to-face with potential new customers without any marketing expense or hassle on your part.</li>\n        <li>Steady business. Maintain a steady cash flow, no matter the season.</li>\n        <li>Customer feedback. Get a clear picture of how you're doing. Use your Select Home Warranty customer survey reports to improve customer satisfaction.</li>\n      </ul>\n    </p>\n"},
